Let's face them together.

00:00:32.164 --> 00:00:35.854
I don't know why, but you look kind of familiar.

00:00:36.109 --> 00:00:38.215
You don't remember being….

00:00:38.509 --> 00:00:39.311
Being what?

00:00:39.422 --> 00:00:42.350
You're saying Wave is a prince?

00:00:42.669 --> 00:00:43.235
Yes.

00:00:43.235 --> 00:00:46.671
It's also my first time feeling love for someone.

00:00:46.827 --> 00:00:48.291
I love you too.

00:00:52.738 --> 00:00:53.788
Sleepy? Then go get some sleep.

00:00:59.487 --> 00:01:01.096
I woke up super early for this,

00:01:02.119 --> 00:01:03.306
so I have to watch it.

00:01:04.329 --> 00:01:05.516
I'll wait and see.

00:01:06.227 --> 00:01:07.312
Thanks, though.

00:01:08.157 --> 00:01:09.782
I've wanted to see the sunrise.

00:01:11.338 --> 00:01:14.843
It feels like a new beginning.

00:01:15.466 --> 00:01:17.502
But I like sunsets more.

00:01:19.792 --> 00:01:22.755
Sunsets are pretty too,

00:01:23.222 --> 00:01:26.444
but they can feel sad sometimes.

00:01:28.178 --> 00:01:31.728
But once the sun rises, everything lights up

00:01:32.583 --> 00:01:34.536
it feels like there's hope.

00:01:35.470 --> 00:01:37.046
No matter how bad things get,

00:01:37.623 --> 00:01:38.933
you can always start again.

00:01:41.512 --> 00:01:42.533
What if…

00:01:43.467 --> 00:01:47.130
What if your family were millionaires?

00:01:49.101 --> 00:01:50.829
What if you had a really warm home,

00:01:51.807 --> 00:01:54.202
and someone who truly loved you
was waiting for you?

00:01:56.514 --> 00:01:57.726
What if you were—

00:02:03.440 --> 00:02:04.842
If that's the case, that sounds nice too.

00:02:05.909 --> 00:02:07.642
If I really were a millionaire,

00:02:08.331 --> 00:02:14.207
I'd build schools and charities
for poor kids who love music.

00:02:15.963 --> 00:02:19.085
But I'm happy with my life now.

00:02:21.286 --> 00:02:23.945
Sitting here watching the sunrise
with someone I love—

00:02:25.701 --> 00:02:28.882
no money could buy this happiness.

00:02:30.727 --> 00:02:31.709
Got it.

